╔══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╗
║  HELIX TRAINER — Exercise 9.2: LSP Commands                     ║
║  Category: Space Mode            Difficulty: ★★★ Advanced       ║
╚══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════╝

COMMANDS TO LEARN
─────────────────
  Space k   Hover documentation (show type/docs popup)
  Space s   Document symbol picker (outline)
  Space S   Workspace symbol picker (all files)
  Space d   Go to diagnostic (error/warning)
  Space D   Workspace diagnostics picker
  Space r   Rename symbol (LSP)
  Space a   Code actions (quick fixes, refactoring)
  Space h   Select all references to symbol

INSTRUCTIONS
────────────
  Match each development task to the correct Space command.

────────────────────────── PRACTICE ──────────────────────────────

TASK                                              COMMAND
──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
See the type/docs for a function:                 ???
Jump to a function in this file (outline):        ???
Find a symbol across the whole project:           ???
Jump to the next error/warning:                   ???
See all errors in the workspace:                  ???
Rename a variable everywhere:                     ???
See quick fix suggestions:                        ???
Select all usages of a symbol:                    ???

────────────────────────── EXPECTED ──────────────────────────────

TASK                                              COMMAND
──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
See the type/docs for a function:                 Space k
Jump to a function in this file (outline):        Space s
Find a symbol across the whole project:           Space S
Jump to the next error/warning:                   Space d
See all errors in the workspace:                  Space D
Rename a variable everywhere:                     Space r
See quick fix suggestions:                        Space a
Select all usages of a symbol:                    Space h

──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
HINTS (read only if stuck):
  Hint 1: Space k = knowledge (hover docs)
  Hint 2: Space s = symbols (document), Space S = Symbols (workspace)
  Hint 3: Space r = rename, Space a = actions
  Hint 4: Space h = highlight (select all references)
